headline: 3 Reasons to Sell WAT and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: While the broader market has struggled with the S&P 500 down 1.7% since September 2024, Waters Corporation has surged ahead as its stock price has climbed by 13.1% to $382.94 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
